title: 1987-05-21 Festival Hall, Osaka - FLAC
description:
Iron Maiden
Festival Hall
Osaka, Japan
21 May 1987
 
This was the very last show of the Somewhere on Tour 86/87.

The recording is a little rough, but the performance is enjoyable nonetheless.  Bruce was obviously very drunk, and judging by the frenetic playing, the rest of the band were inebriated, too! 

1.  Intro/Caught Somewhere in Time
2.  2 Minutes to Midnight
3.  Wrathchild
4.  Children of the Damned
5.  Stranger in a Strange Land
6.  Wasted Years
7.  Rime of the Ancient Mariner
8.  Heaven Can Wait
9.  Phantom of the Opera
10. Hallowed Be Thy Name
11. Iron Maiden
12. The Number of the Beast
13. Run to the Hills
14. Running Free
